com.team.web.service.impl

Class UserServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team.web.service.impl.UserServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserService

    @Service
public class UserServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserService
    A Service which serves for handling User performances to the database (Which on this project, stored in Engine.getUsers()).

    This service is ready for future use of database implementations.

      • addCompany

        public java.util.Optional<User> addCompany(CompanyDTO companyDTO)
        Validates the request of adding a company, and adds it in case of success validation. The validation may fail in case there is already a Stock with that Symbol in the Engine.getStocks().
        Specified by:
        addCompany in interface UserService
        Parameters:
        companyDTO - DTO for the Stock to calculate its worth, to add to the User, and to the Engine.getStocks() database.
        Returns:
        In case of success, returns Optional of the requesting User. In case of fail, returns Optional of null.
